FADE IN:

EXT. MOUNTAIN ROAD - DUSK

A single car winds along a switchback road, headlights cutting through fog.

INT. CAR - CONTINUOUS

RENA (40s, weathered, sharp-eyed) grips the wheel.

RENA
Almost there.

Her passenger, silent, stares out the window.

